venue.address_1: Corner of Elm and Auburn Sts.
venue.name: Soon-to-be Murphy's

item.description:
John McCain is launching his campaign in Manchester at Veterans Park this Wednesday. RonPaulHQ will be there to make sure New Hampshire voters know there's a real maverick in the race.

Bring signs if you've got them; we'll have some on hand.

Meet at 4:45pm at the corner of Elm and Auburn (outside what will be Murphy's Taproom). We'll walk over to the park at 5.
item.name: McCain official kick-off, Manchester
